To pass audio inputs to vLLM for multimodal inference, you can use the `audio_url` parameter instead of the `image_url` parameter. Here's how:

```python
chat_completion_from_url = client.chat.completions.create(
    messages=[{
        "role": "user",
        "content": [
            {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "What's in this audio?"
            },
            {
                "type": "audio_url",
                "audio_url": {
                    "url": audio_url
                },
            },
        ],
    }],
    model=model,
    max_completion_tokens=64,
)
```
